# Concrete bibliography references rendered in lessons and connected to usages.
#
# Add lesson-facing citations here: chapters, whole books cited directly, web pages, videos,
# articles, and theses. Reuse `person:*`, `org:*`, and `work:*` nodes from the other fragments
# instead of duplicating metadata. When a reference belongs to a larger container (chapter in a
# book, article in proceedings, paper in a journal), point to that parent with `schema:isPartOf`;
# use direct `schema:publisher` links only when the reference does not depend on a reusable
# container node in `03-works.ttl`.
@prefix schema: <https://schema.org/> .
@prefix dibs: <https://dibs.ravenhill.cl/vocab#> .
@prefix ref: <https://dibs.ravenhill.cl/bibliography/ref/> .
@prefix person: <https://dibs.ravenhill.cl/bibliography/person/> .
@prefix org: <https://dibs.ravenhill.cl/bibliography/org/> .
@prefix work: <https://dibs.ravenhill.cl/bibliography/work/> .
@prefix usage: <https://dibs.ravenhill.cl/bibliography/usage/> .

